<br>
I have no idea what the spawn times are for most of the stuff there.  I've raided in PoG all of twice, because both times I went there we ended up spending more time doing corpse recovery than we did killing.<br>
<br>
However, I DO solo there a fair bit.  Mostly stuff near the entrance, as it gives KILLER exp and PoG is very suiting to both charm-kiting and chant-kiting for bards.  No SoW problems, can't be rooted if we take reasonable precautions, outrun summon before they can hit us, etc.<br>
<br>
